Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the case seems to have closed. but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(8% 25)\NRed Horse in the Fire\NCase Solved Part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's already 3:00 pm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll just have to forget\Nabout Tropical Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
