Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that if we do as you-say,\Nfire could be ignited automatically...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the burn on that light bulb...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could be something that coincidentally\Ngot there during the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that trick were to be used...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any of the three could've done it,\Ncouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner of that house\NAkira Morozumi, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That womanizer Misao Soga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as Ryoko's older\Nsister. Keiko Gondo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,seem to have frequently gone\Nin and out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to Mr. Genda's house\Nto find out who the culprit is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so let's hurry and go into the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may find a diary or something\Nthat could be a key to the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't even have a search wainrant,\Nand-yet you have-the keys-It's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told Genda that\NI would prove his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he broke out in tears\Nand lentÂ«it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is a big house for\NMr. Genda to be living in alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was living here with his mother\Nafter his father passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but last year his mother also\Npassed away of an illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way. Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,did you notice the\Nshoe marks in the corridor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the shoe marks of someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are Mr. Gendas shoe marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the shoes\Nthat's in the shoes cabinet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that.. Mr. Genda...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,take a look at this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something strange\Nin the waste basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soiled socks and a burnt shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Genda's sleepwalking habit\Nwas getting worse, maybe his saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other me did it". is not\Nall that much of a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not that kind of a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not the kind of man that\Nwould set fire to other people's houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuminaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kudo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the telephone bill that wD\Non top of the shoes cabinet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says 30.000 yen a month!\NIsn't it a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's strange for a guy\Nwho's living alone but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran also talks to Sonoko\Nfor a long time over silly things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the bill totals to about that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,silly Kazuha does the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She talks for a long time with mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why women like to\Ntalk on the phone so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That our phone calls are so silly!!
