Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you guys were\Neavesdropping from the front door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't do something\NIow class like that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!!
