Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Radio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,=Itvs inside this vase!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a wiretap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,exactly the same as the vase that is in\Nthe front entrance of the Morozumi's. isn't its?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard other things too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about the wastebasket
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's got be one near\Nthis waste basket too. a wiretap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? A crystal ball...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time inside the cushion\Nunder the crystal ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. I've seen that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the crystal of good luck\Nthat the woman fortuneteller
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at the building in front\Nof Haido Station is selling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's known for being pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! That small cushion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a different color.but similar to the one\NRyoko was holding. don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be in here too?!
