Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iithe guyfGenda-confessed.\NBut suddenly refused to say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red horse was indeed\Nhand-made by Genda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he refuses to say anything\Nabout the serial arsons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And. we're at Gendafs. house rightÂ» now.\NBut can't find any vital evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:08:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda saying that he has a habit of\Nsleepwalking is probably a lie too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the forensic officers\Nwill be here tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm sure something will come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When something more concerning\Nthe investigations: come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it okay. sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just great. Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...what are you up to anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making fake calls like that\Nto all three suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fake calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're fake calls, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found wiretaps in\Nthe vase at the front entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as something in the cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is proof everywhere that Mr. Genda\Nhad a habit of sleepwalking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll explain everything later...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And us being here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't that make more work\Nfor the forensic officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
